course_description: Building on competencies in advanced nursing practice with high-risk neonates and older infants up to age 2, emphasis is on collaboration with health professionals, innovative faculty/student models to enhance student learning of acute and critical care management and stabilization.
prerequisites: NRSG 651 or equivalent transfer credit as prerequisite.
